whereas.text:
Whereas the goal of National Kids to Parks Day is to
			 empower young people and encourage families to get outdoors and visit the parks
			 of the United States;

Whereas communities across the United States offer a
			 variety of natural resources and public land, often with free access, to
			 individuals seeking outdoor recreation;

Whereas the people of the United States should encourage
			 young people to lead a more active lifestyle, as too many young people in the
			 United States are overweight or obese;
